videos.description: Michigan's Isaiah Livers drives towards the basket and finishes the difficult lay-up, getting the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Livers surges to the rim, gets the foul) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Livers surges to the rim, gets the foul

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson finds the cutting Eli Brooks who flushes the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Brooks throws it down

videos.description: Michigan's Jon Teske blocks Armando Bacot's shot, leading to the high-flying layup for Isaiah Livers on the other end.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Teske's block leads to layup for Michigan) 2019/11/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Teske's block leads to layup for Michigan

videos.description: Michigan's Eli Brooks delivers the clutch 3-pointer to put the Wolverines up 72-61 over the Tar Heels with 1:12 remaining in the second half.
videos.headline: Brooks delivers the dagger
